page.title: 19CHILD'S EYE VIEW 1985.
page.content: There are lots of insects that sting fly, crawl and other things as well. In the world there are lots of shops,houses,people,cars,trees,fields, birds and fish.Workmen are building new houses so people can live in them and other things are happening in the world.Most people have got jobs but some haven't because unemployment is quite high. Most people can have food but in Ethiopia there is a famine and water is short. England is a free country and we can do most things we like.If people are bad or do something which is against the rule then they are fined or put in prison.
